Uh. Establishing a dialogue with our community, the Chicano community, um, in an effort to bridge the gaps that have been, uh, uh, uh, caused, bridge the, the, the divisions that have been caused by, uh, the racism that's very often a result of, um, an academy, um, which is very hierarchical and one which, uh, is institutionally and structurally hostile to the presence of minorities, uh, and other minor, marginalized people. With this, I would just like to say, que viva la raza y adelante. We're gonna win this one. Thank you.
